<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Listing Suspended — AddressGuru</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f6f7fb;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
            background: #f6f7fb;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #fff;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: #f59e0b;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header img {
            width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #fafafa;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #f7941d;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">
                    <img src="https://www.addressguru.in/images/logopng.png" alt="AddressGuru Logo">
                </a>
                <h1>Listing Suspended</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Hi <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
                <p>
                    Your listing <strong>“{{listingTitle}}”</strong> has been suspended temporarily due to policy
                    violations or pending verification.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you believe this is a mistake or wish to resolve the issue, please contact our support team at <a
                        href="mailto:support@addressguru.ae">support@addressguru.ae</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                &copy; {{year}} AddressGuru. All rights reserved. <br>
                <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">addressguru.ae</a> | <a
                    href="mailto:support@addressguru.ae">support@addressguru.ae</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>